\ker\Phi=\{(a,\varphi)\;|\; \Phi((a, \varphi),(b, \psi))=0\;\forall (b, \psi)\in W\times W^*\}
\varphi(b)=0,\quad\forall b\in W\Rightarrow \varphi=0^*
